@startuml

autonumber
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor "Utente" as User
box "Frontend (Client)" #LightBlue
    participant "RegisterForm" as UI
end box

box "Backend (Server)" #LightYellow
    participant "/api/register" as API
end box

box "Database" #LightGreen
    database "PostgresDB" as DB
end box

User -> UI: Inserisce Nome, Email, Password
User -> UI: Clicca "Register"
activate UI

UI -> API: POST {name, email, password}
activate API

group Verifica Esistenza
    API -> DB: FindUser(email)
    activate DB
    DB --> API: Risultato (null o User)
    deactivate DB
end

alt Utente esiste già
    API --> UI: 400 Bad Request ("User already exists")
    UI --> User: Mostra errore a video
else Nuovo Utente
    API -> API: Hash Password (bcrypt)
    API -> DB: CreateUser({name, email, hashedPassword})
    activate DB
    DB --> API: Success
    deactivate DB

    API --> UI: 201 Created
    deactivate API
    UI --> User: Redirect to /login
    deactivate UI
end

@enduml